=\"formValidation\">{Message:validation}</span></div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"form-row\">\n		<div class=\"col-6\">\n			<div class=\"form-group rsform-block rsform-block-personaldata{PersonalData:errorClass}\">\n				<label class=\"control-label formControlLabel\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" title=\"{PersonalData:description}\">{PersonalData:caption}<strong class=\"formRequired\">*</strong></label>\n				<div class=\"formControls\">\n					{PersonalData:body}\n					<div><span class=\"formValidation\">{PersonalData:validation}</span></div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"col-6\">\n			<div class=\"form-group rsform-block rsform-block-recaptcha{reCAPTCHA:errorClass}\">\n				<label class=\"control-label formControlLabel\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" title=\"{reCAPTCHA:description}\" for=\"reCAPTCHA\">{reCAPTCHA:caption}</label>\n				<div class=\"formControls\">\n					{reCAPTCHA:body}\n					<div><span class=\"formValidation\">{reCAPTCHA:validation}</span></div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"form-row\">\n		<div class=\"col-12\">\n			<div class=\"form-group rsform-block rsform-block-send{Send:errorClass}\">\n				<label class=\"control-label formControlLabel\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" title=\"{Send:description}\" for=\"Send\">{Send:caption}</label>\n				<div class=\"formControls\">\n					{Send:body}\n					<div><span class=\"formValidation\">{Send:validation}</span></div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</fieldset>', '[[{\"columns\":[[\"2\",\"1\",\"26\",\"3\",\"23\"]],\"sizes\":[\"12\"]},{\"columns\":[[\"24\"],[\"25\"]],\"sizes\":[\"6\",\"6\"]},{\"columns\":[[\"8\"]],\"sizes\":[\"12\"]}],[]]', 'bootstrap4', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '', '', 'RSForm! Pro example', 1, 0, 'en-GB', '', 1, 1, 1, 0, '<p>Dear {FullName:value},</p><p> thank you for your submission. One of our staff members will contact you by  {ContactBy:value} as soon as possible.</p>', 1, '<p>Dear {FullName:value},</p><p> we received your contact requ